---
title: Sesame-Peanut Pork Chow Mein with Snap Peas
description: This tasty sesame pork chow mein checks all the boxes for the ultimate takeout fake-out meal! Crisp snap peas, sesame-spiked pork and chewy chow mein noodles are all tossed in a savoury oyster-hoisin sauce!
